dialogues = Array[String](["Right on time.", "Your mission as a planet hauler is to use the magnetic grabber to move the planets I designate to their new star.", "You may ask, 'Why ?'. The star that they currently orbit is coming to an end very soon. And if they're still around when it dies they'll be perfects preys for all the entities lurking in the darkness of the universe...", " However, you don't need to worry about yourself as your ship is designed to keep them far away from you. ", "Anyway, you probably already know what this job involves, so let's start with this inhabitate planets just there.", "Good luck."])

